-- Sodexo Increases Full-Year Forecasts for Revenue Growth, Operating Profit
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-07T05:03:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/sodexo-increases-full-year-forecasts-for-revenue-growth-operating-profit.html

          
          
             Sodexo SA said that full-year 2009-10
sales will show an organic increase of about 2 percent, raising
its forecast from a previous prediction of growth of between 0.5
percent and 1 percent.  
 Full-year operating profit will be between 780 million
euros and 800 million euros, it said in a statement on its
website.  
          
          


  


        